<L>__{exterior construction site dawn}
<A>__{the rising sun flares behind the towering silhouette of an unfinished building, deserted in the early morning light. high up, a monkey his head around a girder. four stories below, other monkeys are climbing.}
<L>__{exterior shopping mall dawn}
<A>__{deserted in the first light of dawn, the stores face each other across a broad promenade with blank staring windows. nothing happens. for a long moment. then, an african bull elephant appears, turning the corner, lumbering toward us along the promenade, raising his trunk to trumpet triumphantly to the other elephants trotting into view behind him.}
